FBIS4-37628 "drnes121_o_94002" FBIS-NES-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 SYRIA Voices Regret at Bloodshed Voices Regret at Bloodshed JN2206155494 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1515 GMT 22 Jun 94 JN2206155494 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Excerpts] President Hafiz al-Asad received 'Abd-al-'Aziz 'Abd-al-Ghani, member of the Yemeni Presidential Council, at 1215 today. [passage omitted] Talks dealt with the situation in Yemen. The president expressed Syria's regret for the course of events in Yemen as well as Syria's concern over the continued bloodshed. Syria, he added, appeals to all Yemeni brothers to cease fire and resort to dialogue. [passage omitted]
